This is a book about beauty, passion, a longing for the thing that a true artist or lover of the arts, especially music, craves and feels, the fire that burns within.
A book that dares to take one, if one dares to take that step, on a journey deep into the bare souls of it's characters.
The story that unfolds is not a story that has a specific plot, or develops into dramatic changes for the characters.
